"{\"uid\": \"newstalk.com-news-thousands-welcome-home-irelands-most-successful-olympic-team-ever-1754277\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Live  19:00-22:00  15.27 12 Aug 2024  Share this article  15.27 12 Aug 2024  Share this article  Ireland's Olympians have receieved a rapturous welcome home in Dublin today.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 97, \"end\": 104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999981700405814, \"rank\": 1.8299534669834722e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 160, \"end\": 166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9995943020903508, \"rank\": 0.00040583956357406504, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Never before has Team Ireland brought home so many medals- four golds and three bronzes.\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999683951, \"rank\": 2.723464223197575e-11, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressed in their green and white gear, athletes arrived at Dublin Airport to cheers and requests for autographs and high fives.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards they were taken to O'Connell Street where an estimated 20,000 people had gathered to celebrate their achievements.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Home sweet home ?\\u2728#TeamIreland|#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/68YYeSTtth  - Team Ireland (@TeamIreland)August 12, 2024    \\\"Dublin is alive with pride this afternoon,\\\" reporter Josh Crosbie toldLunchtime Live.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9995943020903508, \"rank\": 0.00040583956357406504, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The tourists must think we celebrate St Patrick's Day every Monday .\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Patrick\", \"score\": 0.7269557490309629, \"rank\": 0.3329087816369775, \"text\": \"Patrick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Patrick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Patrick\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am standing outside the GPO - this is where the stage has been set up - and I am looking down now and it's just a sea of Irish flags.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 824, \"end\": 827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Post_Office\", \"score\": 0.9898234617597703, \"rank\": 0.01005366740464709, \"text\": \"GPO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Post_Office\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Post_Office\"}, {\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.5779846459015758, \"rank\": 0.7297520801875481, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are county colours there as well, I can see some Tipperary hats, some Donegal flags, Kilkenny jerseys - people have come from near and far to welcome home Team Ireland today.\\\"\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tipperary_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9995801837812462, \"rank\": 0.0004199923235920834, \"text\": \"Tipperary\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tipperary_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tipperary_GAA\"}, {\"begin\": 1012, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Donegal\", \"score\": 0.9861781346506416, \"rank\": 0.014015567092376734, \"text\": \"Donegal\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Donegal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Donegal\"}, {\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilkenny_GAA\", \"score\": 0.884869995702552, \"rank\": 0.13010189205110526, \"text\": \"Kilkenny\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilkenny_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilkenny_GAA\"}, {\"begin\": 1097, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999683951, \"rank\": 2.723464223197575e-11, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_Today\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ireland today\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_Today\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the first ever homecoming parade of its kind and gold medalist Daniel Wiffen said he hoped Ireland's success would lead to more people getting involved in sport.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1218, \"end\": 1225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999981700405814, \"rank\": 1.8299534669834722e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It means so much, honestly,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think everyone does their sport to try and inspire somebody and to hear that so many people are starting to swim\\u2026 It seems like we have had a real big impact on the whole of Ireland.\\\"\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1507, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999981700405814, \"rank\": 1.8299534669834722e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Limerick athlete Sarah Lavin said they were all blown away by the support shown by Irish fans this year.\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\", \"score\": 0.9999540160706658, \"rank\": 4.1037245882414805e-05, \"text\": \"Limerick\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\"}, {\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Lavin\", \"score\": 0.9999913449620929, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Lavin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Lavin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Lavin\"}, {\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.5779846459015758, \"rank\": 0.7297520801875481, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[It's] amazing,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That crowd, it's so touching - to come back to this, I can not believe it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Due to the homecoming parade, a series of traffic restrictions are in place outside the GPO.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1823, \"end\": 1826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Post_Office\", \"score\": 0.9898234617597703, \"rank\": 0.01005366740464709, \"text\": \"GPO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Post_Office\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Post_Office\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Connell Street is closed fully until 5.30pm, when one lane will open, with the rest to follow after 10pm.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1829, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4343643688233586e-48, \"text\": \"O'Connell Street\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Northbound traffic is being redirected through Eden Quay and southbound traffic is being moved towards Gardiner Street.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2041, \"end\": 2056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gardiner_Street\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gardiner Street\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gardiner_Street\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gardiner_Street\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LUAS stops on both the Red and Green lines are closed between Smithfield and the Point, and Dominick and Stephen's Green.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2121, \"end\": 2131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Smithfield\", \"score\": 0.9999997683151192, \"rank\": 1.240351809605232e-07, \"text\": \"Smithfield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Smithfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Smithfield\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, Dublin Bus has published a long list of route diversions on its website.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2191, \"end\": 2201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_Bus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dublin Bus\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_Bus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_Bus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Main image: Boxer Kellie Harrington showing fans her medal on O Connell Street during the Team Ireland celebrations.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2283, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kellie Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 2355, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999683951, \"rank\": 2.723464223197575e-11, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Photo: Leon Farrell/\\u00a9 RollingNews.ie  Share this article  Read more about  Most Popular  Related  Download the Newstalk App  \\u00a9 